</page>

<expt main>
/ preinstructions = (start)
/ blocks = [1 = consent; 2 = calibration; 3 = instructions; 4-12 = practice; 13 = end_practice; 14-266 = experiment; 267 = followup]
/ postinstructions = (end)
</expt>

<page end>
^^Thank you for your participation!
</page>

